Source: pg-regresql
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/boringsql/regresql

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-regresql
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-regresql
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Trust pg_class statistics for query planning instead of physical file size
  pg_regresql forces the PostgreSQL planner to use catalog statistics from
  pg_class for query planning instead of physical relation size estimates.
